cc:Work.dc:title: Compact Fluorescent Lamp
cc:Work.dc:description: Compact fluorescent lamp drawing realistic. It is a general idea to use the incandescent lamp to represent graphically an idea, suggestion or proposal. With the Compact Fluorescent Lamp, I suggest to support the use of new technologies that, indeed, will improve the social wealth in all the world even in those countries in where access to technology is really difficult.
